{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an exciting adventure of epic proportions inspired by the rich folklore of south-eastern Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this turn-based roguelike card battler, take the role of a miller\u2019s offspring, their life upended during a vicious raid, and shape their place in a war-torn medieval world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find companions to help you overcome adversity, train, collect, and equip your party with better gear to give yourself an edge in the tests ahead. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Fresh Spin on the Deckbuilding Genre</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your equipment and training dictate what cards are available, how many, and how powerful they are. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/card-on-item-v3.gif?t=1733413090\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tactical Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We fused dynamic initiative, simple positioning, turn delay, and turn-based card play into a rich and rewarding combat experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/tactical-combat.gif?t=1733413090\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Varied Card Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not all cards are created equal; some are actions the characters will take during their turn, while others are reactive and must be kept in hand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/card-battle.gif?t=1733413090\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Character Progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage your party's training to better prepare them for the trials that await them. Only through focused training combined with battle experience will they progress from novices to masters of their weapons of choice. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your actions will determine how people will remember you. Will they sing heroic ballads in every tavern, or will they whisper tales untold about your infamous exploits?   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only time will tell if your stories will become Unsung Ballads.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2366240?t=1733413090","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2366240?t=1733413090","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733413090","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733413090","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,2,5],"notes":"The core gameplay mechanic of Unsung Ballads depicts cartoon characters fighting each other to death while wearing costumes that might be considered revealing. \r\nThe story contains mature themes, ranging from psychological torment, bullying, and discrimination to senseless violence and war. It also describes abuse of fantasy drugs and alcohol. "},"detailed_description":"<h1>Try it before you buy it!</h1><p>You can try our game via the Open Playtest. Just &quot;Request Access&quot; above and it will be granted instantly.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an exciting adventure of epic proportions inspired by the rich folklore of south-eastern Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this turn-based roguelike card battler, take the role of a miller\u2019s offspring, their life upended during a vicious raid, and shape their place in a war-torn medieval world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find companions to help you overcome adversity, train, collect, and equip your party with better gear to give yourself an edge in the tests ahead. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Fresh Spin on the Deckbuilding Genre</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your equipment and training dictate what cards are available, how many, and how powerful they are. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/card-on-item-v3.gif?t=1733413090\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tactical Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We fused dynamic initiative, simple positioning, turn delay, and turn-based card play into a rich and rewarding combat experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/tactical-combat.gif?t=1733413090\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Varied Card Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Not all cards are created equal; some are actions the characters will take during their turn, while others are reactive and must be kept in hand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/card-battle.gif?t=1733413090\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Character Progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage your party's training to better prepare them for the trials that await them. Only through focused training combined with battle experience will they progress from novices to masters of their weapons of choice. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your actions will determine how people will remember you. Will they sing heroic ballads in every tavern, or will they whisper tales untold about your infamous exploits?   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only time will tell if your stories will become Unsung Ballads.</p>","developers":["Read Play Code"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse